      <div class="grid grid-col-1 gap-4 mt-5">
        <InfoItem
          client:visible
          title="How do I download the software?"
          description="You can choose one of the software in our universal catalog. After clicking on the 'Download' button, a window will open in which the program will be described."
        />
        <InfoItem
          client:visible
          title="Am I downloading the software for free?"
          description="Yes, it's absolutely free. You can download any software you like and download them at high speed without registration, torrents and SMS."
        />
        <InfoItem
          client:visible
          title="Why is the archive under a password?"
          description="Crack is already installed in the downloaded software, because of this, Windows Defender and other antiviruses swear at it. Don't worry, we check all the software before publishing them."
        />
        <InfoItem
          client:visible
          title="What about viruses?"
          description="Don't worry, we check the published software very carefully, viruses are excluded."
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
